  "texts": [
    "Let ⊑ be the restriction.For any p-semilattice ⟨A, ≤⟩ and x ∈ A, x ≤ x * *, so we need only show that x * * ≤ x.",
    "If x * * = ⊥, then x * * ≤ x, so suppose x * * ̸ = ⊥.",
    "Then we claim that x * * ⊑ s x (Definition 4.1).",
    "For suppose z ⊑ x * *, so z ≤ x * * and z ̸ = ⊥.",
    "Then z ∧ x ̸ = ⊥, for otherwise z ≤ x *, contradicting z ≤ x * * and z ̸ = ⊥."
  ],
